      "content": "hey quick question. i started taking these antibiotics for a skin infection 3 days ago (it was pretty red and swollen) but honestly im feeling way better today. like it's basically gone. is it okay if i just stop taking them now so i dont have to keep putting all these chemicals in my system if i dont need them?",
