      "content": "i get that, but my doctor didn't even mention resistance, they just said take them for 10 days. if the redness and swelling is totally gone, isn't that proof the bacteria is already dead? it feels like a lot of unnecessary medicine to take for another week if there's no actual infection left to fight.",
